Now we will move on to our next
exercise where we will actually

86
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:16,660
construct the tabs example
that you saw earlier.

87
00:07:16,660 --> 00:07:20,196
So we're going to go into
the aboutus.html page,

88
00:07:20,196 --> 00:07:25,955
we're gonna use tabbed navigation to build
the tab navigational elements there,

89
00:07:25,955 --> 00:07:30,727
and then we're gonna organize
the content inside tabbed panes, and

90
